slike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"恭喜晒，香港無事，唔使你地羨慕上街，羨慕唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e37a3f8619378c7533538505a28540900b5e909","tid":1413934,"uid":17799,"like":134,"dislike":0,"score":134,"quote":{"pid":"e094c7357821a3891b8e2c53ecee7dd66a0af9ed","tid":1413934,"uid":214192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"乜法案嚟㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"政府調六百億設立投資公司，令人想起末代澳<br />\n督韋奇立在澳門回歸前幾個月將五千萬公帑調到葡國設立「私人」基金會。最終，五千萬當然係去如黃鶴。<br />\n那時政府窮，資源不多，所以巧取豪奪都只是拿走五千萬。但回歸二十年，澳門政府庫房水浸，所以要咬，一咬就六百億。<br />\n六百億是多少？當然是天文數字。澳門今年的現金分享，七十五萬居民所分的合共只是73.54億。若六百億全部用作現金分享，每位永久居民可以分到八萬幾。如今卻交給一間公司去投資，邊個專才咁把炮？虧損風險邊個付？諗下都牙煙！"},{"pid":"75815a0a36a4e7e958cea3618af157b4a15f5c45","tid":1413934,"uid":17799,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"949d06001d489852cc6eaa45f884427ad753c795","tid":1413934,"uid":12628,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"恭喜晒，香港無事，唔使你地羨慕上街，羨慕唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"講緊澳門上街遊行呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e367d8e16c2f2d923ce980cdc12f00b0fb8fc31","tid":1413934,"uid":17799,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:23:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母崔屎安 淆底安"},{"pid":"ae8e7cb2f44e0f0b85fbbaeff0c3121f70fa67cb","tid":1413934,"uid":258578,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa6bef626570c552e6853a2a910fda318fb771f2","tid":1413934,"uid":17799,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ae8e7cb2f44e0f0b85fbbaeff0c3121f70fa67cb","tid":1413934,"uid":258578,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"屌 淆底安 食屎狗 做野做到